reviewText: I have retired my roto-tiller, thanks to the advise on mulching with rotton hay from Ruth Stout.  Would have loved to meet her, my kind of gal- no nonsense ! !

This is a tribute to Ruth Stout. You get to see her garden--not during the growing season however. I watched this video many times on youtube. It's fun to see Ruth Stout in action in her hay covered garden.
